    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's interesting that you mention the dark suit as the \"standard.\" so, if someone was wearing traditional attire from like east asia or africa to a big international business meeting, would that be seen as \"unprofessional\" even if it's high quality and formal in their own culture? or is there a way to incorporate that into a \"sophisticated\" look without losing that professional baseline you mentioned?",
